high_descs: Walk to the left side of the sink that's on the right.
Pick up the lettuce that's in front of the butter knife.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the right.
Open the door of the fridge, place the lettuce on the shelf to the right of the tomato, close the fridge door, wait a few seconds, take the lettuce out of the fridge, and close the fridge door.
Turn right and face the sink on the right.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
Walk straight and make a right to face the counter.
Take the lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn right and walk straight making another right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce on the second shelf next to the tomato and shut the door. Open it again and take out the lettuce.
Turn to the right and walk straight making a right to face the sink again.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the lettuce off the counter to put in the fridge to put in the sink.

high_descs: walk straight to the counter by the sink
Grab the cabbage on the counter
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator
Open the the refrigerator, put the cabbage in the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, take the cabbage out, close the refrigerator
Turn right, walk to the sink on the right
Put the cabbage in the sink
anns.task_desc: cool the cabbage in the refrigerator, put it in the sink

high_descs: Go forward and turn to the right to the counter where the lettuce is.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside, close the fridge, then open the fridge, remove the lettuce, and close the fridge.
Turn to the right and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.
